{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "There\u2019s still no action-application path in the backend, only parsing and event logging. I\u2019m checking whether the repo already has selection/update services I can reuse; if not, I\u2019ll add the policy engine as a standalone evaluator first...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_25", "text": "There\u2019s still no action-application path in the backend, only parsing and event logging. I\u2019m checking whether the repo already has selection/update services I can reuse; if not, I\u2019ll add the policy engine as a standalone evaluator first and give it an API surface that the future mutating endpoint can call directly.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 53, "prompt_index": 33, "prompt_name": "32 \u2014 UI Action Policy Engine", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T05:00:37-07:00"}
